Pizza Sales Dashboard

This project presents a visual dashboard of pizza sales data from January 15 to December 15.


 Key Insights
- Total Revenue: $817.86K  
- Average Order Value: $38.31  
- Total Orders: 21,350  
- Total Pizzas Sold: 49,574  
- Average Pizzas per Order: 2.32

 Breakdown
- Best Sales Day: Friday (3.5K orders)
- Top Pizza Category: Classic (14,888 sold)
- Most Popular Size: Large (45.89%)

 Tools Used
- Power BI / Excel (for visualization)
- GitHub (for version control & hosting)
